And clearly thinks some players aren't giving it their all: &quot;He (Sanchez) is always eager, he always wants to win, he is always fighting. It&rsquo;s a way of telling the team: &ldquo;if you do not want to be like that, then I&rsquo;m leaving.&rdquo; I think that&rsquo;s just what Alexis wanted to show.&quot;<br />
<br />
It's not Wenger he's furious with, doesn't think he should go: &ldquo;Not for me. The club must sign quality players. That is what they have to do. This club has a lot of money, but has to buy.&rdquo;

